  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    A[Start Peroxisome Biogenesis] --> B(Environmental Inducers)\n    A --> C(Cellular Metabolic Demand)\n    B --> D(Oleate/Fatty Acid Presence)\n    C --> D\n    D --> E[Activate PEX Genes & Peroxisomal Enzyme Genes]\n\n    E --> F[Transcription Factor Binding (e.g., Oaf1/Pip2)]\n    F --> G[mRNA Synthesis for PMPs & Matrix Proteins]\n    G --> H[Ribosomal Protein Synthesis]\n\n    H --> I[Nascent PMPs in Cytosol]\n    H --> J[Nascent Matrix Proteins in Cytosol]\n\n    I --> K[Pex19 Chaperone Binding to PMPs]\n    K --> L[Cytosolic PMP-Pex19 Complex]\n\n    J --> M[Pex5/Pex7 Binding to Matrix Proteins]\n    M --> N[Cytosolic Matrix Protein-Pex5/Pex7 Complex]\n\n    O[Pre-existing Peroxisomes Present?] --> |No| P[ER-derived Pre-peroxisomal Vesicle Formation]\n    O --> |Yes| Q[Existing Peroxisome]\n\n    P --> R[ER Membrane]\n    R --> S[Pex3 & Pex16 Insertion into ER]\n    S --> T[Budding of Pex3/Pex16 Vesicles]\n    T --> U[Pre-peroxisomal Vesicle]\n    \n    L --> V[PMP Insertion Target?]\n    V --> |To Pre-peroxisome| U\n    V --> |To Existing Peroxisome| Q\n\n    U --> W[PMP Insertion into Membrane]\n    Q --> W\n    W --> X[Pex3 (PMP Receptor)]\n    W --> Y[Pex16 (PMP Receptor)]\n    L --> Z[Pex19 (PMP Chaperone)]\n    \n    W --> AA[Peroxisomal Membrane]\n    AA --> AB[PMP Integration into Peroxisomal Membrane]\n\n    N --> AC[Peroxisomal Membrane Docking (Pex14)]\n    AC --> AD[PTS1 or PTS2 Pathway?]\n    AD --> |PTS1| AE[PTS1 Protein-Pex5 Complex]\n    AD --> |PTS2| AF[PTS2 Protein-Pex7 Complex]\n    \n    AE --> AG[Pex5 (PTS1 Receptor)]\n    AF --> AH[Pex7 (PTS2 Receptor)]\n    AC --> AI[Pex14 (Docking Protein)]\n\n    AJ{All for Matrix Import?}\n    AG --> AJ\n    AH --> AJ\n    AI --> AJ\n    AJ --> AK[Matrix Protein Translocation into Lumen]\n\n    AK --> AL[Peroxisomal Lumen]\n    AL --> AM[Enzyme Complex Assembly in Lumen]\n\n    AE --> AN[Pex5 Ubiquitination (Pex2/10/12 RING complex)]\n    AN --> AO[Recycling of Pex5 to Cytosol]\n    AF --> AP[Recycling of Pex7 to Cytosol]\n\n    AB --> AQ[Lipid Synthesis & Import]\n    AQ --> AR[Peroxisome Membrane Expansion]\n    AR --> AS[Peroxisome Elongation]\n    AS --> AT[Pex11 (Proliferation Factor)]\n    AT --> AU[Peroxisome Fission Initiation]\n\n    AV[Fission Components Present?]\n    AU --> AV\n    AW[Dnm1 (Fission Dynamin)] --> AV\n    AX[Vps1 (Fission Dynamin)] --> AV\n    AV --> AY[Peroxisome Fission]\n    AY --> AZ[New Daughter Peroxisomes]\n    \n    AM --> BA[Post-translational Modifications (PTMs)]\n    BA --> BB[Regulation of Peroxisome Activity/Stability]\n    \n    BC{Peroxisome Maturation Complete?}\n    AB --> BC\n    AK --> BC\n    AQ --> BC\n    AM --> BC\n    BC --> BD[Mature Functional Peroxisome]\n\n    AZ --> BD\n    BD --> BE[Peroxisomal Metabolic Reactions]\n    BE --> BF[Metabolic Products (e.g., Acetyl-CoA, H2O2)]\n    BF --> BG[Cellular Homeostasis]\n    BD --> BH[Peroxisome Turnover (Pexophagy)]\n    BH --> BG\n\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style A fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style B fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style G fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style H fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style I fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style J fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style K fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style L fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style M fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style N fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style O fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style P fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Q fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style R fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style S fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style T fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style U fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style V fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style W fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style X fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n   